    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300011798_19_982-1039",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "982-1039",
      "markText": "州县地方政府便形成了一种特殊格局：不断更替且缺乏经验的州县官“领导”着一帮久居其职、久操其事且老于世故的当地书吏。",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300011798&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=982&rangeEnd=1039",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9d327e0813ab6b1bg018167?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=982&rangeEnd=1039"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300011798_9_3772-3854",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "3772-3854",
      "markText": "简言之，在由官府设立的各类乡村单元中执行特定行政职能的首领，仅仅是官府的代理人，由州县官任命，受州县官控制。不能把他们当成代表村民的乡间领袖。自治在城乡都是不存在的",
      "totalCount": 270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300011798&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=3772&rangeEnd=3854",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9d327e0813ab6b1bg018167?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=3772&rangeEnd=3854"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300011798_10_1722-1818",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "1722-1818",
      "markText": "一省之内的所有官员，从总督、巡抚到州县官，都由吏部任命。虽然省级长官可以就下属官员的晋升、降级、免职提出建议，但建议必须按吏部确定的规则和程序提出，且研拟每一人事案并作出正式决定的只能是吏部。",
      "totalCount": 204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300011798&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1722&rangeEnd=1818",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9d327e0813ab6b1bg018167?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1722&rangeEnd=1818"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300011798_4_2767-2846",
